@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-5 mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h4 class="mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h4>
        <p>We collect personal information such as your name, email address, and any other data you provide during registration or while using our services.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h4 class="mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
        <p>We use your information to provide and improve our services, send notifications, and personalize user experience. Your data is never sold or shared with third parties without your consent.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h4 class="mb-3">3. Data Security</h4>
        <p>We implement security measures such as encryption and access controls to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h4 class="mb-3">4. Your Rights</h4>
        <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal data. To make a request, please contact us through the contact form or support email.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h4 class="mb-3">5. Changes to This Policy</h4>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and significant updates will be communicated to users.</p>
    </section>

    <p class="text-muted small">Last updated: August 1, 2025</p>
</div>
